@withregram • @master_gigi Onto book 14 of 2023. I’m actually backtracking a few books since Eye of God was the 1st James Rollins book I ever read. Found it at the airport. Looked good and interesting for a 9 hour flight. I found out much later that it was part of a series. Since I read it years ago, I don’t remember a whole lot and how it ties in the order, so I’m going to re-read it. If you like history, archeology, action, things that blow up, secret military/ government agencies, and the fantastical, then James Rollins is an author you should check out. 

